fun fact:
a lot of us interpreted “how can i love the heartbreak, you’re the one i love” as this person who couldn’t accept the breakup because they love the other person.

the more accurate (or literal) translation from korean lyrics of it would be “oh how could i have even (to the extent) love the heartbreak? (it’s because) you’re the one that i love”
